      <title>Northvolt 解决延误问题，斯堪尼亚加快电动卡车产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/scania-ramps-up-e-truck-production-as-northvolt-fixes-delays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典卡车制造商 Scania CV AB 正在加大电动卡车的产量，因为之前 Northvolt AB 延迟供应的电池已经开始大量运抵其位于​​南泰利耶的工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/scania-ramps-up-e-truck-production-as-northvolt-fixes-delays</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
